      {
        "text": "To use UUI services, you need to wrap your application into the "
      },
      {
        "text": "UuiContext.Provider",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " React context, which passes the services to the application, so that they can be accessed."
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "data": {},
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "This React context is also required for the proper work of several components. E.g.: "
      },
      {
        "text": "Button",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " requires routing context to make SPA redirects.  "
      },
      {
        "text": "Dropdown",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " and "
      },
      {
        "text": "ModalWindow",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " need "
      },
      {
        "text": "LayoutContext",
        "uui-richTextEditor-code": true
      },
      {
        "text": " to get appropriate layer z-index."
      }
    ]
  }
